Rescue

Restart a long running error-first callback function on error.

    Discussion:     http://github.com/bigeasy/rescue/issues/1

    Documentation:  http://bigeasy.github.io/rescue
    Source:         http://github.com/bigeasy/rescue
    Issues:         http://github.com/bigeasy/rescue/issues

    Install:        `npm install rescue`

    License:        MIT

To learn everything you want to know about Rescue start here:

    http://bigeasy.github.io/rescue
